sudo apt-get install libssl-dev

Download and Install RStudio Desktop from https://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download/
After install RStudio, Open it

> install.packages("swirl")
> library("swirl")
> swirl()
> install_from_swirl("R_Programming_Alt", dev = FALSE, mirror = "github")
> swirl()   select 2 to "R Programming Alt"



